        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 border-b-2 border-red-600 pb-2">ğŸ¯ Best Practices</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">âœ… Do This</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">âœ“</span>
                <span><strong>Be specific</strong> about learning objectives</span>
