              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">âœ“</span>
                <span><strong>Use enhancement mode</strong> for research-based improvements</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">âœ“</span>
                <span><strong>Review and edit</strong> the generated prompt before using</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">âœ“</span>
                <span><strong>Test with your AI tool</strong> and refine as needed</span>
