          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4">ğŸ”§ Advanced Features</h3>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">âš¡ Improve This Prompt</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">After generating a prompt, make it even better:</p>
              <ol class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>1. Click "Improve This Prompt"</li>
                <li>2. Select desired improvements</li>
                <li>3. Apply selected enhancements</li>
                <li>4. Edit the result if needed</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">ğŸ“‹ Copy and Customize</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Make the prompt your own:</p>
              <ol class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>1. Review the generated prompt</li>
                <li>2. Edit directly in the text box</li>
                <li>3. Copy to clipboard when ready</li>
                <li>4. Save for future reference</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
